<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/113311-god-s-teeth-isn-t-anyone-else-bothered-by">God&#39;s teeth! Isn&#39;t anyone else bothered by how the inhabitants of London speak modern English? I mean sure, it&#39;s maybe a wee bit more formal than Diana&#39;s, but otherwise quite obviously not Elizabethan English. (Does Harkness not think we can handle it?)</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_113311'><a id="like_count_community_question_113311" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/113311?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">28 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11559200-shadow-of-night">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/113311-god-s-teeth-isn-t-anyone-else-bothered-by">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/113311-god-s-teeth-isn-t-anyone-else-bothered-by">See all 19 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
