<span id="freeTextContainer4506418927966616238">What a wonderful, vibrant, rich exciting thriller/mystery/love story this is.<br/>Loved how the supernatural is woven through the story as Diana and Matthew journey through Elizabethan Europe. <br/>A cracking read, and a worthy sequel to DoW. Can&apos;t wait for the next one.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText4506418927966616238" style="display:none">What a wonderful, vibrant, rich exciting thriller/mystery/love story this is.<br />Loved how the supernatural is woven through the story as Diana and Matthew journey through Elizabethan Europe. <br />A cracking read, and a worthy sequel to DoW. Can't wait for the next one.<br /></span>
